  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare blood loss between using low dose (500 mg) and high
      dose (3 g) topical intra-articular tranexamic acid after total knee arthroplasty in
      double-blind RCT
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
